{"tid":2455142,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"傳英有意播哈里專訪逾90分鐘未曝光片段 「奧花製作公司知道他們坐在金礦上」","createTime":"2021-03-20T23:05:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-20T23:38:54.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"323143da4bed15d3136c5bcddbaa2aa7b792e98d","tid":2455142,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T23:05:35.000Z","msg":"專訪本月7日在美國哥倫比亞廣播公司（CBS）首播，翌日在ITV播出。梅根指皇室人員種族歧視、活於皇室時想過自尋短見等，引起全球議論。<br />\n<br />\nCBS說全球近5,000萬人收看專訪，ITV錄得1,240萬人收看。<br />\n<br />\n專訪有逾90分鐘片段仍未曝光。英國《星期日人物報》（Sunday People）引述行內消息人士，有人對足本播放專訪興趣盎然，說專訪首播時，已是本年至今英國最大騷，各地電視台都有買入播映權&hellip;&hellip;播多一些肯定也肯定是收視冠軍。奧花的製作公司知道他們坐在金礦上，故交易可能已經完成。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210321/JSVLQ5XXNFFGHPDT4M222RUNVM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210321%2FJSVLQ5XXNFFGHPDT4M222RUNVM%2F&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfaVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=b49a80ff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210321%2FJSVLQ5XXNFFGHPDT4M222RUNVM%2F&h=078886e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210321/JSVLQ5XXNFFGHPDT4M222RUNVM/</a>"},{"pid":"f35e7c874537817862702c33166fc7e4855f83a5","tid":2455142,"uid":183758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T23:38:54.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">死力架屌你老母趁地淋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"}]}